https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/acvTBuTY2Hx8L2LNzJB0luRq0RK.jpg Hand-crafted from paper art by Brittney Lee, Walt Disney Animation Studios’ acclaimed visual development artist on “Frozen” and “Frozen 2,” this warm and inviting hearthside scene sets a festive holiday mood. Stylized cut-out paper flames combine with imaginative visual effects (including a touch of snow provided by Elsa) and silhouetted images of Anna, Elsa, Olaf, Kristoff, and Sven to add to your holiday fun and enjoyment.
